This module implements lifting for type-bound operations (=sink, =copy, =destroy, =deepCopy, =wasMoved, =dup).

Imports

modulegraphs, lineinfos, idents, ast, renderer, semdata, sighashes, lowerings, options, types, msgs, magicsys, ccgutils, trees
